{
  "stem": "166.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "That was, they called, the [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "The [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And after this, there was no room where to put us again.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So they put us in the shop, also-- in a wood shop.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "In a wood shop, they put in.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "They again pressed in so many people in that room.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Maybe 1,000 people they pressed in in that barrack, staying with whips at the door and hitting.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So when they hit, that creates pressure.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Everybody's pushing, pushing in.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So they pushed in so many people in there-- and it was raining outside cats and dogs-- until the whole floor collapsed from pressure.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it collapsed down to the basement.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And everybody's sliding down like this.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I start to bite feet, because my hands were full of people on top of me.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I don't know how we survived.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "People are stronger than-- it's impossible to think how would-- how we survived.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] After this, they took us out from there and-- half of them got killed.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Half of them are dead.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "After this, they took us into tents.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we stayed there in the tents maybe a week.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then it got-- more people died and more died.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So it got room.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We got into a barrack later.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It got room so we got into a barrack, because people were dying.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I stayed in the barracks, and I found my-- a cousin of mine there.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I say I'm going to stay with him together.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We're holding hands.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I was so lucky.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "It was my mother's sister's son.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And he came from another camp, also, there-- transit.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And he was an upholsterer.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "So he-- they were calling.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "They needed upholsterers.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "So I said I'm going to say I'm an upholster, also.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
